The Shi'ar possess technologies common to most alien races, including:

* '''[[Shi'ar Imperial Fleet (Earth-616)|Intergalactic Warp-Capable Starships]]:''' Ranging in size from small vessels to ships approximately 100 miles long (e.g. [[Apocalypse-Class Behemoth]]).{{r|Uncanny X-Men Vol 1 481}}
* '''Teleportation Systems'''{{r|X-Men: Kingbreaker Vol 1 4}}
* '''Holographic Technology'''{{r|Uncanny X-Men Vol 1 476}}
* '''Robots'''{{r|Uncanny X-Men Vol 1 485}}
* '''Artificial Intelligence'''{{r|X-Men Vol 1 108}}
* '''Cybernetics'''
* '''Superdestroyer:''' A planet breaking class of battleship used to sterilize life sustaining biomes in the service of the Shi'Ar.{{r|New X-Men Vol 1 124}}
* '''[[Stargate]]s:''' Create stable wormholes for travel, either in a planet or in space.{{r|X-Men Vol 1 105}}
* '''Force Fields'''{{r|Uncanny X-Men Vol 1 485}}
