* '''Shi'Ar Antimatter Engine:''' A device that functions as a workable power source, used by the new [[Krakoa (Earth-616)|Mutant Nation]] to operate [[Cerebro]].{{r|Powers of X Vol 1 5}}
* '''[[Logic Diamonds|Shi'ar Logic Diamonds]]''': Mineral utensils with infinite information storage space. Used by Krakoa to facilitate they're resurrection protocols.{{r|Powers of X Vol 1 5}}

