*'''Galactic-level Weapons:''' Super-powerful [[Nega-Bombs]] used to devastate a dwarf galaxy (the Greater Magellanic Cloud), the home galaxy of the [[Kree Empire]] during the rule of Majestrix [[Lilandra Neramani (Earth-616)|Lilandra]].{{r|Wonder Man Vol 2 8|9}}{{r|Avengers Vol 1 347}}
